description: With his packing almost finished, Roman Eros is all set for his big trip, but there's just one more thing he needs before he leaves. Roomie Princeton Price has a pretty good idea of what Roman is hoping for, and thinks he might be able to give Roman the fond farewell he wants. Luckily for him, Roman saved just enough room for what Princeton is packing, and has no problem squeezing him in. Princeton, in turn, makes sure to give a Roman a going away present he'll remember, one that will definitely make sure Roman is ready to cum back when his trip is over.
title: Packin' To Go
